msgid "Direction"
msgstr "Smer"

#: ../../tutorials/direction.rst:4
msgid ""
"There is a compass on the BBC micro:bit. If you ever make a weather "
"station use the device to work out the wind direction."
msgstr ""
"V BBC micro:bite sa nachádza kompas. Ak by si niekedy robil(a) meteostanicu,"
" môžeš použiť zariadenie na určenie smeru vetra."

